task.persona: A distinguished professor in Computer Science specialized in data transmission

instruction.level1: Schedule a research meeting with the data transmission team on May 18th at 2PM
instruction.level2: Create an event on May 18th at 2PM titled "Research Meeting with Data Transmission Team."
instruction.level3: Create an event titled 'Research Meeting with Data Transmission Team' on May 18th at 2 PM.

steps: Click the Create button to start creating a new event
Select 'Event' from the create menu to start setting up a new event.
Enter the event title 'Research Meeting with Data Transmission Team'
Open the date and time settings to change the event date to May 18th.
Fill the event start date with May 18th.
Fill in the event start time with '2:00 PM'
Click the 'Save' button to finalize the creation of the event.
